a work-related injury claim.

581
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:42,881
They're demanding the company

582
00:28:43,040 --> 00:28:45,320
cover all medical expenses directly,

583
00:28:45,441 --> 00:28:46,040
as well as

584
00:28:46,161 --> 00:28:48,481
work injury-related costs.

585
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:49,800
Plus compensation.

586
00:28:50,201 --> 00:28:50,721
Mr. Zhou.

587
00:28:50,984 --> 00:28:51,681
Mr. Zhuang.

588
00:28:51,681 --> 00:28:52,481
