657
00:31:28,441 --> 00:31:29,401
What happened to her?

658
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:34,800
She's my first friend at Jun An.

659
00:31:35,040 --> 00:31:36,241
If she's in trouble,

660
00:31:36,641 --> 00:31:37,520
