in the hospital for almost a week

682
00:32:26,401 --> 00:32:27,481
and hasn't woken up at all.

683
00:32:28,241 --> 00:32:28,961
Xiaoyu.

684
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:30,961
How are you holding up?

685
00:32:31,681 --> 00:32:32,641
I'm at the hospital

686
00:32:32,921 --> 00:32:34,080
with Ms. Wang,

687
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,280
Zhubao's mom.

688
00:32:36,161 --> 00:32:38,441
Xiaoyu, I'll make this short.

689
00:32:38,641 --> 00:32:39,641
Ms. Wang might not

690
00:32:39,641 --> 00:32:41,921
want to apply
for a work injury certification.

691
00:32:42,201 --> 00:32:43,401
She wants Yiaiwan Tech

692
00:32:43,721 --> 00:32:45,520
to cover all the medical expenses.

693
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:47,241
Plus some compensation.

694
00:32:47,441 --> 00:32:49,800
We are Yiaiwan Tech's legal counsel.

695
00:32:49,840 --> 00:32:51,320
And the firm has confirmed that

696
00:32:51,320 --> 00:32:52,721
we're handling this case.

697
00:32:53,040 --> 00:32:54,201
Right now, you need to

698
00:32:54,201 --> 00:32:55,961
report the conflict of interest
to Mr. Zhou

699
00:32:55,961 --> 00:32:57,840
and get yourself out of this mess.

700
00:32:58,080 --> 00:32:58,760
Also, for now,

701
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,721
stop meeting with Zhu Zhisheng's family.

702
00:33:01,481 --> 00:33:02,961
I'll report to Mr. Zhou.

703
00:33:05,481 --> 00:33:07,600
But Zhubao is from
a single-parent household.

704
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:09,360
His mom can't

705
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:10,320
look after him alone.

706
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:11,481
We need to take shifts.

707
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:17,360
Xiaoyu, is it worth it if Zhu Zhisheng

708
00:33:17,721 --> 00:33:18,681
really cheated on you?

709
00:33:19,441 --> 00:33:21,201
I just want him to wake up.

710
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:23,040
I don't care about anything else.

711
00:33:23,401 --> 00:33:24,520
I just don't understand.

712
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:26,120
How did everything change

713
00:33:26,120 --> 00:33:27,760
in just over a month?

714
00:33:28,001 --> 00:33:29,120
A perfectly healthy man

715
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:30,921
is now lying in a hospital bed.

716
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:33,280
I've known him for over a decade

717
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:34,560
and dated him for four years.

718
00:33:34,961 --> 00:33:36,560
Even if he fell for someone else,

719
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:38,721
our feelings for each other were real.

720
00:33:38,721 --> 00:33:39,961
I can't just abandon him.

721
00:33:40,520 --> 00:33:41,080
But

722
00:33:41,080 --> 00:33:43,481
