723
00:33:43,560 --> 00:33:44,800
It's way too complicated.

724
00:33:45,161 --> 00:33:46,481
Don't do anything foolish.

725
00:33:46,481 --> 00:33:48,201
You'll only get yourself in trouble.

726
00:33:49,001 --> 00:33:50,921
Xiaoyu, listen to me.

727
00:33:51,201 --> 00:33:52,080
Remember

728
00:33:52,401 --> 00:33:54,560
what you told me
during the Warm Nest case?

729
00:33:54,921 --> 00:33:56,520
Win-win is the best outcome.

730
00:33:56,921 --> 00:33:58,520
We understand how you feel.

731
00:33:58,641 --> 00:34:00,120
But you've got to protect yourself.

732
00:34:09,288 --> 00:34:11,400
(Conflict of Interest)

733
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:13,576
(Lawyers must not
represent clients in cases)

734
00:34:13,576 --> 00:34:16,584
(where there is a conflict of interest
with themselves or their law firm.)

735
00:34:20,481 --> 00:34:21,600
She's not in a good place.

736
00:34:23,361 --> 00:34:24,321
The past few days

737
00:34:24,321 --> 00:34:25,680
have hit her way too hard.

738
00:34:25,736 --> 00:34:26,401
She even asked

739
00:34:26,401 --> 00:34:28,200
if she had made the wrong choice.

740
00:34:28,640 --> 00:34:29,560
I think she regretted

741
00:34:29,560 --> 00:34:31,120
joining the Talent Hunt Program.

742
00:34:31,441 --> 00:34:33,040
If she starts blaming herself

743
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:34,240
for Zhu Zhisheng's coma,

744
00:34:34,720 --> 00:34:36,441
no one can stop her downward spiral

745
00:34:36,761 --> 00:34:37,881
into guilt.

746
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:39,961
Why is it her fault?

747
00:34:40,040 --> 00:34:41,600
How is any of this her fault?

748
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:44,281
Why are women so prone to reflection?

749
00:34:44,281 --> 00:34:45,720
She did absolutely nothing wrong.

750
00:34:45,720 --> 00:34:46,841
She's brilliant.

751
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:49,120
Why is she reflecting on herself?

752
00:34:49,160 --> 00:34:50,481
What's there to reflect on?

753
00:34:51,200 --> 00:34:53,321
Didn't Zhu Zhisheng
prioritize his career?

754
00:34:53,401 --> 00:34:54,240
He didn't choose

755
00:34:54,240 --> 00:34:55,841
to come to Beijing for Guo Xiaoyu.

756
00:34:56,232 --> 00:34:56,841
Listen.

757
00:34:56,841 --> 00:34:57,961
We must stop her

758
00:34:57,961 --> 00:34:59,361
from doing anything foolish.

759
00:34:59,720 --> 00:35:01,200
If nobody can stop her, I will.

760
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:04,520
If I were Guo Xiaoyu.

761
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:05,680
I wouldn't choose Zhubao.

762
00:35:07,361 --> 00:35:07,961
I'd choose you.

763
00:35:10,160 --> 00:35:11,080
No offense.

764
00:35:11,120 --> 00:35:12,361
But I don't date lawyers.

765
00:35:12,640 --> 00:35:13,361
No thanks.

766
00:35:13,361 --> 00:35:14,160
I'm off to work.

767
00:35:23,321 --> 00:35:25,520
Mr. Zhuang, I spent all day researching

768
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:27,841
labor dispute cases
between companies and employees,

769
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:30,680
especially work injury
compensation claims.

770
00:35:31,040 --> 00:35:32,321
And I did preliminary research

771
00:35:32,321 --> 00:35:33,921
on Yiaiwan's case.

772
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:35,881
Plus, my classmate from the UK

773
00:35:35,881 --> 00:35:38,120
