784
00:36:01,321 --> 00:36:03,401
You owe it to your own efforts.

785
00:36:03,761 --> 00:36:04,680
We have no reason

786
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:06,401
to eliminate a talented employee.

787
00:36:08,640 --> 00:36:09,841
So I'm not here

788
00:36:09,881 --> 00:36:11,881
to ask for privileges.

789
00:36:11,961 --> 00:36:13,801
I'm here to earn this opportunity

790
00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:15,801
through my hard work.

791
00:36:16,321 --> 00:36:16,961
You know

792
00:36:16,961 --> 00:36:18,680
I've always wanted to
join Mr. Song's team.

793
00:36:19,080 --> 00:36:20,200
This is a rare chance.

794
00:36:20,321 --> 00:36:22,640
I want to prove my capabilities
through this case.

795
00:36:34,801 --> 00:36:35,841
Not bad.

796
00:36:36,401 --> 00:36:37,600
Full of doubt yesterday

797
00:36:37,761 --> 00:36:38,961
