810
00:37:05,120 --> 00:37:06,841
Right now, I just want this opportunity

811
00:37:07,160 --> 00:37:08,680
to join Mr. Song's team.

812
00:37:09,640 --> 00:37:10,520
I'll get by for now.

813
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:11,160
Someday,

814
00:37:11,160 --> 00:37:12,600
I'll figure out what I want.

815
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:13,881
I'm impressed.

816
00:37:14,160 --> 00:37:15,720
A bottle of champagne for celebration.

817
00:37:16,441 --> 00:37:18,080
Sorry, but I've quit drinking.

818
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:19,881
Alcohol doesn't solve everything.

819
00:37:20,160 --> 00:37:21,921
Plus, there's alcohol poisoning.

820
00:37:22,040 --> 00:37:22,792
It's not worth it.

821
00:37:23,281 --> 00:37:24,801
But I've gotten into boxing now.

822
00:37:24,841 --> 00:37:25,761
More competitive.

823
00:37:25,921 --> 00:37:27,656
It feels great,
just like being a lawyer.

824
00:37:29,361 --> 00:37:30,560
I dare not cross you now.

825
00:37:31,001 --> 00:37:32,680
I'm a law graduate after all.

826
00:37:32,881 --> 00:37:34,361
I wouldn't resort to violence.

827
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:36,264
